definition: that's all/just this and nothing more
and/as well as/and so/but (not)/yet (not)/(indicates causal relation)/(indicates change of state)/(indicates contrast)

sentences.english: That's it. No file is being imported.
sentences.chinese: 仅此而已，没有任何文件被导入。

sentences.english: But the ability to segment data does not end there.
sentences.chinese: 不过，细分数据所能做到的并非仅此而已。

sentences.english: At home, you can go to the beach, but that's about it.
sentences.chinese: 在我的家乡，你可以去海滩，但也就仅此而已。

sentences.english: When conversing, I just hear the words. That’s all.
sentences.chinese: 在和人谈话时，我听的是别人说的话，仅此而已。

sentences.english: The seeds and dirt, a prayer for rain, that I can use.
sentences.chinese: 种子和泥土，向老天祈雨，仅此而已。
只是一篇补白，仅此而已。

sentences.english: Viserys was Mad Aerys's son, just so.
sentences.chinese: 韦赛里斯是疯王伊利斯的儿子，仅此而已。

sentences.english: There are some solutions that come with lunar calendars for China and Middle East countries, but that's about it.
sentences.chinese: 当然在中国和中东地区国家会提供阴历，但仅此而已。

sentences.english: Just a bad dream, that's all.
sentences.chinese: 只是做了一个恶梦，仅此而已。

sentences.english: My job was just to get the ball, if it rebounded from the basket. That's all.
sentences.chinese: 我的任务就是抢篮板，仅此而已。

sentences.english: We were none the worse for our terrible experience.
sentences.chinese: 我们有过一次可怕的经历但仅此而已。

sentences.english: A man can get away with wearing one ring, and that's it.
sentences.chinese: 男人戴一枚戒指还勉强能让人们接受，仅此而已。

sentences.english: They provided the essentials of education but nothellong beyond.
sentences.chinese: 他们提供教育的要端，但仅此而已。

sentences.english: At the federal level, things are better—but only a bit.
sentences.chinese: 联邦法院相比之下情况稍好，但也仅此而已。

sentences.english: “Smile and stay out of it” works every time.
sentences.chinese: “笑一下，仅此而已”这一招每次都很有用。

sentences.english: I sort of remember the last 10-20,000 years and that's it.
sentences.chinese: 我记得一二万年前的事，但仅此而已。

definition: a modal particle indicating (that's all, only, nothing much)
a modal particle indicating (don't mind it, ok)
to strive one's hardest/to spare no effort
see 沒關係|没关系[mei2 guan1 xi5]
only/merely/nothing but/no more than/it's just that ...
to be indifferent/not to matter/cannot be said to be
